    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I'm not sure if the problem I experienced on Unity 2020.3.10 is exactly the same as yours, but it seems that the error content is very similar. In the end, I solved the problem in this way: install a newer version of gradle (version 6.8.1), and then change the path of gradle in Unity's external tool to the path I installed. Build, the problem is solved.</p>\n"
